metadata.name: Christmas Crypto Copium 2022
metadata.description: A lot of us are rekt this year because of the idiots whose crypto ponzis imploded. On the tree you'll find SBF, Caroline of FTX, founders of bankrupt 3 Arrows Capital, Terra and Celsius. It's been a real shitshow this year! Let's hope next year will be less idiotic. One of the presents I got this year was censorship yay! The cryptoart saints in the background are Colborn of MOCA, Beatriz of Dada and Rizzle. The cats with knives are there because one day I found a knife sticking in the floor and our cats looked guilty af.
